Subject: [PATCH 50/97] backend-drm: Support modifier

Tested on rk3588 with:
unset WESTON_DISABLE_ATOMIC
export WESTON_ALLOW_GBM_MODIFIERS=1
export DRM_PLANE_TYPE_152=primary
export DRM_PLANE_TYPE_128=overlay
weston&

